ballot_measures.number: Prohibit Government Closure of Places of Worship During Emergencies Amendment
ballot_measures.title: Prohibit Government Closure of Places of Worship During Emergencies Amendment
ballot_measures.description: Prohibit the government from closing gatherings at places of worship during declared emergencies, including public health emergencies. This legislatively referred constitutional amendment is on the Wisconsin 2026 ballot.

ballot_measures.number: Prohibit Government Discrimination or Preferential Treatment Amendment
ballot_measures.title: Prohibit Government Discrimination or Preferential Treatment Amendment
ballot_measures.description: Prohibit the government from discriminating or granting preferential treatment based on race, sex, color, ethnicity, or national origin. This legislatively referred constitutional amendment is on the Wisconsin 2026 ballot.

ballot_measures.number: Prohibit Partial Veto to Increase Tax or Fee Amendment
ballot_measures.title: Prohibit Partial Veto to Increase Tax or Fee Amendment
ballot_measures.description: Prohibit the governor from using the partial veto to create or increase any tax or fee
